---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Styles" description="Visual style guidance and the tokens that back it">
  <section class="gw-section">
    <div class="gw-width gw-stack--lg">
      <div class="gw-prose">
        <h1 class="gw-heading-l">Styles</h1>
        <p>Styles combine usage guidance with the semantic tokens that back each visual decision. Components reference these tokens; designers use them as the closed scale of choices available.</p>
        <p>Per-style pages (colour, spacing, type, layout) are not yet written. See the <a class="gw-link" href="/get-started/architecture/">architecture overview</a> for how tokens are layered.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</DocsLayout>
